[SN]TITLE[SN]
In pictures: Life on Instagram

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Since its launch in 2010, the photo-sharing site Instagram has grown at a phenomenal rate, with nearly 100 million pictures and videos being posted everyday.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The images capture everything from personal moments to be shared with friends and family to large public events, image curation on a global scale.
Penguin art director Jim Stoddart has pulled together a selection of those that caught his eye, for publication in a book.
Life on Instagram, curated by Jim Stoddart, is published by Particular Books.
